    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seeps and a suspension that feels a bit tired over bumps. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the roof, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. It is a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics and is willing to keep up with basic ongoing maintenance.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style with this fantastic find! This car is in good condition and has been clearly well-cared for, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience you can count on. It's a clean, dependable vehicle that\u2019s ready for its next adventure\u2014come see why this well-maintained beauty is the perfect choice for your next ride!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The body shows heavy wear, including several large dents, significant rust patches, and fading clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears, and several interior components are missing or broken. While the engine does start, it runs roughly and the transmission exhibits slipping, making it unsuitable for a daily commute without major repairs. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts, and it is priced accordingly for a quick, as-is sale.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition. The engine and transmission require significant mechanical repair to be fully operational. The exterior has visible body damage and paint deterioration, and the interior shows heavy wear and staining throughout.",
      "price": 5500.0,
